34:10.091 --> 34:11.875
- You're early.

34:12.528 --> 34:14.052
- I can come back later.

34:14.095 --> 34:15.923
- Don't be silly.

34:15.966 --> 34:17.533
Good quality in a person.

34:20.101 --> 34:22.016
- What are we doing here?

34:22.843 --> 34:24.932
- You know the hardest part
of what I do?

34:26.586 --> 34:30.807
Doing a job without anyone
knowing you did a job.

34:33.419 --> 34:34.985
Take JFK for instance--

34:35.029 --> 34:38.250
the grassy knoll,
book depository--

34:38.293 --> 34:41.166
so many theories,
so much confusion

34:41.209 --> 34:43.255
about where
the bullet originated.

34:43.298 --> 34:46.214
It was a perfect hit.

34:46.258 --> 34:47.911
Have a look.

35:01.011 --> 35:02.622
What do you see?

35:03.188 --> 35:08.018
- A Greek deli, a donut shop,
cell phone store, I don't know.

35:08.062 --> 35:09.455
What am I looking at?

35:09.498 --> 35:12.675
- Confusion.
Do you have the time?

35:17.332 --> 35:19.247
- It's 12:00.

35:19.291 --> 35:22.076
- Perfect.
Take another look.

35:45.404 --> 35:47.232
- Say when.

36:00.027 --> 36:01.768
- Anytime you're ready.

36:05.946 --> 36:07.600
- Why is it up to me?

36:07.643 --> 36:11.778
- You hired me to do a job.
- Yeah, so you do it.

36:14.172 --> 36:16.913
- This way,
I'm assured no regrets.

36:16.957 --> 36:19.220
So what's it gonna be?

36:19.264 --> 36:23.224
- ♪ Every time
